 energy (such as the central highlands). These units can be installed on most roof/slabs and is a reliable product designed to last a lifetime.<br />The evacuated tubes (with HEAT PIPE Technology) capture a high degree of solar irradiation by the selective coated inner surface contained within a glass vacuum and transfers it to the heating heads inside the tank via copper rods due to high thermal conductivity. The heads in the tank then heat the water and are stored ready for your use - hot water free from the sun!</p><p><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-3471\" src=\"http://www.sunbird.lk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/10yearswarranty-300x115.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"115\" /></p><p><strong>10 YEAR WARRANTY</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">This product is covered for all manufacturing defects for installation and use within standard parameters for potable water.</p><p><b>1 Year warranty on the Heating Element provided.</b></p>","_id":"f98ae69"},{"tab_title":"Features","tab_content":"<p><strong>System</strong></p><p>\u2022 Vacuum tubes (HeatPipe technology)<br />\u2022 Can be used with a pressure booster pump<br />\u2022 Operating Pressure: 0 ~ 0.6Mpa (6bar)<br />\u2022 Suitable for areas with low sunshine<br />\u2022 No maintenance required<br />\u2022 Winner of Presidential Award in Energy<br />\u2022 Delivery pressure equals input pressure (no friction loss)<br />\u2022 Stainless Steel anchoring brackets for roof/slab<br /><br /><strong>Hot water Storage Tank</strong></p><p>\u2022 Stainless Steel - SUS304 (1mm)<br />\u2022 Long-lasting aluminum outer body<br />\u2022 Electrical Backup (3kw / 1.5kw)<br />\u2022 Machine-injected high-density Polyurethane foam insulation (50mm)<br />\u2022 UV stabilized fiberglass side covers<br />\u2022 Sacrificial Anode - User-replaceable<br /><br /><strong>Solar Collector</strong></p><p>\u2022 Tube glass - Borosilicate<br />\u2022 Heat Pipe Vacuum tube (58x1800mm)<br />\u2022 All aluminum frame<br /><br /><strong>Safety Components</strong></p><p>\u2022 Anti-Vacuum protection assembly<br />\u2022 Electrical thermostat controller (42\u00b0 ~ 55\u00b0C)<br />\u2022 Non-Return valve at the cold water inlet<br />\u2022 Auto Air Relief valve<br />\u2022 Sacrificial Anode<br />\u2022 Auto Pressure/Temperature relief valve<br /><br /><strong>Optional components (to purchase separately)</strong></p><p>\u2022 Auto control valve for delivery temperature<br />\u2022 Remote electronic controller (temperature/ pressure) with display</p>","_id":"448d8cd"}],"border_width":{"unit":"px","size":2,"sizes":[]},"content_color":"#7A7A7A","content_typography_typography":"custom","content_typography_font_family":"Roboto","content_typography_font_weight":"400","_animation":"fadeIn","_background_background":"classic","_box_shadow_box_shadow":{"horizontal":0,"vertical":0,"blur":4,"spread":0,"color":"rgba(0,0,0,0.5)"}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"tabs"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false},{"id":"d4ebafd","elType":"section","settings":[],"elements":[{"id":"a710369","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":100,"_inline_size":null},"elements":[{"id":"93b8366","elType":"widget","settings":{"title":"Module Types","header_size":"h3","title_color":"#0B1473"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"heading"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false},{"id":"8a8afc9","elType":"section","settings":[],"elements":[{"id":"36f8fca","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":100,"_inline_size":null},"elements":[{"id":"31be486","elType":"widget","settings":{"html":"<div class=\"table-responsive\">\r\n<table class=\"dcf-table dcf-table-bordered dcf-table-striped dcf-w-100%\">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"dcf-txt-center\" scope=\"col\" data-label=\"Models\">Models</th>\r\n<th class=\"dcf-txt-center\" scope=\"col\" data-label=\"Capacity/Usage\">Capacity/Usage</th>\r\n<th class=\"dcf-txt-center\" scope=\"col\" data-label=\"Tank Dimensions\">Tank Dimensions</th>\r\n<th class=\"dcf-txt-center\" scope=\"col\" data-label=\"gross wt\